message: |

    hygen {component new} --name {NAME} --prefixTitleStory { or } --name

    Generates a React component with a storybook story and style.

      NAME           The component name in kebab-case (required).
      --name     Generate a stateful component (optional).
      --prefixTitleStory   Generate a functional component (optional).

    If no flags given, will generate a simple component.

    More details about syntax:
        http://www.hygen.io/docs/templates

